sequenceDiagram
  participant U as User Input
  participant A as Agent Builder
  participant T as Delegate Tool
  participant H as Hook Layer
  participant M as Model Route
  participant S as Subagent Session

  U->>A: define prompt intent
  A->>A: compose sections
  A->>T: inject system/user content
  T->>H: inject continuation/context
  H->>M: route by category/model
  M->>S: dispatch promptAsync
  S-->>T: consume result payload
  T-->>U: return formatted output
